tourBios.otherCarHigh: While attending Cleveland State university he was named to the All-Horizon League first team and Horizon League All-Tournament team in 2008... Was the Horizon League Conference champion in 2008 and 2009...Won for tournaments while playing for his college golf team.
tourBios.personal: Favorite quote is "You play to win the game" by Herm Edwards...Dream foursome would include Arnold Palmer, Jack Nicklaus and Ben Hogan...If he weren't playing golf he would be a musician. Hopes to be featured in Rolling Stone to document his musical accomplishments...Biggest thrill outside of golf is working on composing a new Christmas CD...Loves any course designed by Pete Dye...Favorite golf memory was winning the PGA Assistants' Championship, and his favorite place to visit is Toronto. Charity he is involved with is the Steve and Marjorie Harvey Foundation...People may not know that he designs his own golf courses.
